      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 24.7 - 老子 24.9</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 24.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>其在道也，曰餘食贅行。物或惡之，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Such conditions, viewed from the standpoint of the Dao, are like remnants of food, or a tumour on the body, which all dislike.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
