      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 24.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故有道者不處。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Hence those who pursue (the course) of the Dao do not adopt and allow them.</seg>
      </tuv>
